songs.title: Fight For
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics From Snippet

[Chorus]
Stop me, stop me
Please stop me to leave
From your love tonight
Promise if I stay, you'll stay too
Don't wanna fight, fight, fight
Fight for you
I'll do you right, right, right
Right for you
Don't wanna fight, fight, fight
Fight for you
I'll do you right, right, right
Right

[Verse]
I'll be thinking all about
You babe
In the morning till it's getting
Late I could be the one you love
And it's true
[...]
The one you're making love
To

[Chorus]
Stop me, stop me
Please stop me to leave
From your love tonight
Promise if I stay, you'll stay too
Don't wanna fight, fight, fight
Fight for you
I'll do you right, right, right
Right for you
Don't wanna fight, fight, fight
Fight for you
I'll do you right, right, right
Right
